==石花菜科的属==
* ''Acanthopeltis'' Okamura in Yatabe, 1892
* ''Acrocarpus'' Kützing, 1843
* ''Capreolia'' Guiry & Womersley, 1993
* ''Gelidiophycus'' G.H.Boo, J.K.Park & S.M.Boo, 2013
* [[石花菜属|石花菜属]] ''Gelidium'' J.V.F. Lamouroux, 1813
* ''Onikusa'' I. Akatsuka, 1986
* ''Peysonnelia''
* ''Porphyroglossum'' Kützing, 1847
* ''Ptilophora'' Kützing, 1847
* ''Teloedema''
* ''Yatabella'' Okamura, 1900

